00:11:04.440 --> 00:11:06.170
through the tribulations, just like he's

00:11:06.180 --> 00:11:10.310
done for me. I am just human, y'all.

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:13.310
Everybody was asking for prayer,

00:11:13.320 --> 00:11:15.350
and everybody's asking me for

00:11:15.360 --> 00:11:18.170
healing and for all this stuff. I

00:11:18.180 --> 00:11:21.170
don't control the switch; Jesus does. But

00:11:21.180 --> 00:11:23.750
the same Jesus that lives in me

00:11:23.760 --> 00:11:25.670
lives in you.

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:28.069
You have the same power and authority

00:11:28.079 --> 00:11:30.410
living on the inside of you that

00:11:30.420 --> 00:11:32.870
lives in me. Greater is He that is in me

00:11:32.880 --> 00:11:34.490
than he that is in the world. Greater is He

00:11:34.500 --> 00:11:36.110
that is in you than he that is in the

00:11:36.120 --> 00:11:36.889
world.

00:11:36.899 --> 00:11:40.670
Jesus lives on the inside of you.

00:11:40.680 --> 00:11:43.370
It doesn't take me to pray for you; you can

00:11:43.380 --> 00:11:45.769
pray for yourself. You have that

00:11:45.779 --> 00:11:47.630
authority that dwells on the inside of

00:11:47.640 --> 00:11:50.509
you. You can speak to your mountain and

00:11:50.519 --> 00:11:52.310
it will hear you, and it will depart and be

00:11:52.320 --> 00:11:54.110
cast into the sea. It will depart

00:11:54.120 --> 00:11:56.990
from you and be cast into the sea. You

00:11:57.000 --> 00:11:59.150
have mountain-moving faith on the inside

00:11:59.160 --> 00:12:00.430
of you.

00:12:00.440 --> 00:12:04.069
Faith comes by hearing, and hearing by

00:12:04.079 --> 00:12:06.410
the word of God. That's the same way I

00:12:06.420 --> 00:12:08.509
got it. I don't have

00:12:08.519 --> 00:12:10.850
Superman faith. I have faith that has

00:12:10.860 --> 00:12:13.009
been consistent. It's like going to the

00:12:13.019 --> 00:12:16.069
gym. You go and you lift

00:12:16.079 --> 00:12:17.630
the weights.

00:12:17.640 --> 00:12:20.090
You're working out, and you may see small

00:12:20.100 --> 00:12:22.370
results. You may see a little bit

00:12:22.380 --> 00:12:24.949
here and there, but I've seen people

00:12:24.959 --> 00:12:27.710
that are huge bodybuilders and you know

00:12:27.720 --> 00:12:30.230
how they got there? Not by one time going

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:32.690
to the gym, not by two times going to the

00:12:32.700 --> 00:12:36.310
gym, but consistency

00:12:36.320 --> 00:12:39.430
is what brings the results.

00:12:39.440 --> 00:12:42.350
When you are consistent with the word of

00:12:42.360 --> 00:12:44.509
God, when you get the word of God inside

00:12:44.519 --> 00:12:46.690
of you and it's consistency

00:12:46.700 --> 00:12:49.850
every day—every day you're hitting

00:12:49.850 --> 00:12:49.860
it—you

00:12:49.860 --> 00:12:52.370
know those divots in

00:12:52.380 --> 00:12:54.590
the caves, or the little water dripping

00:12:54.600 --> 00:12:57.410
on the rock, and all of a

00:12:57.420 --> 00:12:59.030
sudden over the course of time it

00:12:59.040 --> 00:13:01.790
creates a crater inside of it. That's

00:13:01.800 --> 00:13:04.250
what happens when you keep

00:13:04.260 --> 00:13:06.230
the word inside of you. Like a little

00:13:06.240 --> 00:13:09.050
drip, you keep it in there. If your flesh

00:13:09.060 --> 00:13:11.210
wants to eat three times a

00:13:11.210 --> 00:13:11.220
day—breakfast,

00:13:11.220 --> 00:13:14.449
lunch, and dinner—you should feed your

00:13:14.459 --> 00:13:17.210
spirit some kind of food at least twice

00:13:17.220 --> 00:13:19.970
a day. Get something on the inside of you.

00:13:19.980 --> 00:13:23.090
How desperate are you for change in your

00:13:23.100 --> 00:13:24.829
life?

00:13:24.839 --> 00:13:27.290
People say, 'Oh, I need change in my life.

00:13:27.300 --> 00:13:29.210
I'm spiritually drained. I'm spiritually

00:13:29.220 --> 00:13:31.550
going through all this

00:13:31.560 --> 00:13:33.290
stuff.'How

00:13:33.300 --> 00:13:36.530
desperate are you for that change?

00:13:36.530 --> 00:13:36.540
You've

00:13:36.540 --> 00:13:38.930
got to be desperate. You've got to be

00:13:38.940 --> 00:13:41.690
like a bulldog on a bone. You've got to say,

00:13:41.700 --> 00:13:45.290
'I'm not going to give up until I get my

00:13:45.300 --> 00:13:48.350
miracle. I'm not giving up until I get a

00:13:48.360 --> 00:13:51.050
touch from the Lord.

00:13:51.060 --> 00:13:53.269
I want to hear you,

00:13:53.269 --> 00:13:53.279
Father.'I'm

00:13:53.279 --> 00:13:55.190
telling you, I'm not

00:13:55.200 --> 00:13:57.769
anything special; I've just been diligent.

00:13:57.779 --> 00:14:00.110
I just go and I get in the word.

00:14:03.720 --> 00:14:06.769
I've been desperate. When a man

00:14:06.779 --> 00:14:09.370
can hardly read or write or do anything

00:14:09.380 --> 00:14:11.990
and you see other men

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:14.150
that are able to

00:14:14.160 --> 00:14:15.949
provide for their families and take care

00:14:15.959 --> 00:14:17.990
of their families, it's very

00:14:18.000 --> 00:14:20.449
humbling to me

00:14:20.459 --> 00:14:22.910
because I want to be that. And so I've

00:14:22.920 --> 00:14:25.550
had to press in even harder because of

00:14:25.560 --> 00:14:27.230
the learning problems that I've dealt

00:14:27.240 --> 00:14:29.210
with. I'm getting in the word, saying, 'God,

00:14:29.220 --> 00:14:31.190
show me how to take care of my family.

00:14:31.200 --> 00:14:34.610
Show me what to

00:14:34.610 --> 00:14:34.620
do.'I

00:14:34.620 --> 00:14:36.470
know that you're the provider. I know

00:14:36.480 --> 00:14:37.850
you're the one that provides all my

00:14:37.860 --> 00:14:39.290
needs according to your riches in glory.

00:14:39.300 --> 00:14:41.449
But Father, I thank you that you

00:14:41.459 --> 00:14:44.569
said you blessed my hands

00:14:44.579 --> 00:14:47.629
and anything I put my hands to, I will

00:14:47.639 --> 00:14:50.569
prosper. So I get in those words, I find

00:14:50.579 --> 00:14:52.490
things, I ask Him, 'Father, show me what to

00:14:52.500 --> 00:14:54.889
invest in. Show me what to do.'I look for

00:14:54.899 --> 00:14:58.370
Him every day, all day long. 'God, what do

00:14:58.380 --> 00:15:01.189
you have for me today?'Wake up every day

00:15:01.189 --> 00:15:01.199
anticipating,

00:15:01.199 --> 00:15:03.829
'What's on your agenda

00:15:03.839 --> 00:15:06.889
for my life? Not my agenda, but what's on

00:15:06.899 --> 00:15:08.449
your agenda? What do you want me to do

00:15:08.459 --> 00:15:10.189
today, Lord?'A lot of you might have

00:15:10.199 --> 00:15:12.769
to go to work from eight to five,

00:15:12.779 --> 00:15:14.870
but you can still seek Him for

00:15:14.880 --> 00:15:17.150
what's going on in

00:15:17.160 --> 00:15:19.910
your life. 'Lord, I thank you. I

00:15:19.920 --> 00:15:22.189
submit myself unto you. I just listen to

00:15:22.199 --> 00:15:24.769
you, God. I thank you. I'm desperate. I'm

00:15:24.779 --> 00:15:27.470
hungry, Father. Speak to me. Show me the

00:15:27.480 --> 00:15:29.569
hidden things.'Father, I pray

00:15:29.579 --> 00:15:32.030
Ephesians 1:18 over my mind: 'let the eyes

00:15:32.040 --> 00:15:35.090
of my understanding be enlightened, let

00:15:35.100 --> 00:15:36.829
me know the hope of my calling.'Show me, God, show me what

00:15:36.839 --> 00:15:38.930
you have for me

00:15:38.940 --> 00:15:41.750
today. When you get desperate for

00:15:41.760 --> 00:15:44.870
God, it says those that seek Me

00:15:44.880 --> 00:15:47.269
will find Me. But He wants to see how

00:15:47.279 --> 00:15:49.189
hungry you are. He wants to see how

00:15:49.199 --> 00:15:51.410
desperate you are, because whenever you

00:15:51.420 --> 00:15:53.629
get desperate and you get hungry and you

00:15:53.639 --> 00:15:56.210
start seeking Him, God shows up. But I'm

00:15:56.220 --> 00:15:58.670
going to tell you this: I go to Him a lot

00:15:58.680 --> 00:16:00.949
of times with singing. Last time when

00:16:00.959 --> 00:16:02.870
I sang those songs in the

00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:04.009
last video, that was the first time for

00:16:04.019 --> 00:16:05.810
me to ever sing in public

00:16:05.820 --> 00:16:07.730
to anybody other than my wife and my

00:16:07.740 --> 00:16:09.050
children.

00:16:09.060 --> 00:16:11.769
I sing all the time.

00:16:11.779 --> 00:16:15.530
Praise brings the presence down. Praise

00:16:15.540 --> 00:16:17.689
does. That's a key of

00:16:17.699 --> 00:16:20.389
spiritual warfare: worship. When you

00:16:20.399 --> 00:16:22.610
get in there with thanksgiving... I enter

00:16:22.620 --> 00:16:25.129
into His courts with thanksgiving in my

00:16:25.139 --> 00:16:25.850
heart;

00:16:25.860 --> 00:16:28.069
I enter His courts with praise. I thank

00:16:28.079 --> 00:16:30.170
Him. I thank Him for the electric. Thank

00:16:30.180 --> 00:16:31.970
Him for your water. Thank Him for the

00:16:31.980 --> 00:16:34.850
food you ate. Take time to thank Him and

00:16:34.860 --> 00:16:37.310
worship Him for everything you have. I

00:16:37.320 --> 00:16:39.230
sit there, and in my prayer time, even

00:16:39.240 --> 00:16:40.790
when my son and my wife were all praying,

00:16:40.800 --> 00:16:43.610
I just take a moment. It may be ten

00:16:43.610 --> 00:16:43.620
percent

00:16:43.620 --> 00:16:45.889
of the prayer: 'God, I just want to

00:16:45.899 --> 00:16:47.629
tell you thank you for what you provided

00:16:47.639 --> 00:16:49.730
for me today. Thank you for the clothes

00:16:49.740 --> 00:16:52.850
on my back. Thank you for the shoes on

00:16:52.860 --> 00:16:55.009
my feet. Thank you, Father, that I have air

00:16:55.019 --> 00:16:57.170
in my lungs. Thank you, Lord, that we're

00:16:57.180 --> 00:16:59.269
healed. Thank you, Lord, my children are

00:16:59.269 --> 00:16:59.279
whole.

00:16:59.279 --> 00:17:01.370
Thank you, Lord, for the blessing

00:17:01.380 --> 00:17:04.010
of the trees. Thank you, Lord, for my

00:17:04.020 --> 00:17:06.409
grass out front. Thank you, Lord, for

00:17:06.419 --> 00:17:10.010
the flowers, for the birds, for

00:17:10.020 --> 00:17:13.010
my dogs, for my chickens,

00:17:13.020 --> 00:17:15.049
for everything you've given me.

00:17:15.059 --> 00:17:18.169
God, you've

00:17:18.179 --> 00:17:21.010
been so good to

00:17:21.020 --> 00:17:23.329
me.'You've

00:17:23.339 --> 00:17:26.150
got to get praise down

00:17:26.160 --> 00:17:28.250
inside of your heart. If you want a

00:17:28.260 --> 00:17:30.169
manifestation of the glory of God in

00:17:30.179 --> 00:17:32.270
your house, you've got to be grateful for

00:17:32.280 --> 00:17:34.430
what He's done for you,

00:17:34.440 --> 00:17:37.970
because He's no respecter of persons. And

00:17:37.980 --> 00:17:40.430
if He's going to be good to me, He'll be

00:17:40.440 --> 00:17:42.890
good to you. I'm telling you, God isn't

00:17:42.890 --> 00:17:42.900
going to

00:17:42.900 --> 00:17:44.510
look at me in any other special

00:17:44.520 --> 00:17:45.950
way than you.

00:17:45.960 --> 00:17:49.010
I just take time to worship Him. A lot of

00:17:49.020 --> 00:17:51.710
people are lazy. They don't want to go

00:17:51.720 --> 00:17:54.230
out to the spiritual gym.

00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:56.270
I think it

00:17:56.280 --> 00:17:58.669
sucks to run on a treadmill, but

00:17:58.679 --> 00:18:01.789
some people enjoy it. I don't. But I

00:18:01.799 --> 00:18:04.430
enjoy going to the spiritual gym.

00:18:04.440 --> 00:18:06.830
I like to see the things in the

00:18:06.840 --> 00:18:09.409
spirit. I like to see angels. I like to

00:18:09.419 --> 00:18:10.789
see those things. But I'm going to tell

00:18:10.799 --> 00:18:13.610
you all, I never pursued one time for an

00:18:13.620 --> 00:18:16.250
angel encounter. I never pursued one time

00:18:16.260 --> 00:18:18.650
for a Jesus encounter that I've had, or

00:18:18.660 --> 00:18:21.110
any kind of manifestation. I just seek

00:18:21.120 --> 00:18:22.310
His face. If

00:18:22.310 --> 00:18:22.320
you

00:18:22.320 --> 00:18:25.909
seek His face, you

00:18:25.919 --> 00:18:28.490
can have it. If you seek Him, you can have

00:18:28.500 --> 00:18:30.049
what's in His hand.

00:18:30.059 --> 00:18:32.270
If you seek what's in His

00:18:32.270 --> 00:18:32.280
hand—His

00:18:32.280 --> 00:18:35.630
provision—you

00:18:35.640 --> 00:18:37.010
don't want to do that. You want to seek

00:18:37.010 --> 00:18:37.020
Him.

00:18:37.020 --> 00:18:38.990
You want to seek His face.

00:18:39.000 --> 00:18:41.270
He's not looking for a handout God.

00:18:41.280 --> 00:18:43.190
'I thank you that you give me

00:18:43.200 --> 00:18:44.510
this stuff,'and you're always coming to

00:18:44.520 --> 00:18:46.970
Him whining. He knows what you have need

00:18:46.980 --> 00:18:50.750
of. He knows you're hurting.

00:18:50.750 --> 00:18:50.760
If

00:18:50.760 --> 00:18:54.350
you have something going on in your life,

00:18:54.360 --> 00:18:56.330
come to Him in worship.

00:18:56.340 --> 00:18:59.330
Come to just sing Him a song. 'Lord, I just

00:18:59.340 --> 00:19:01.850
want to sing you a song.'And I just start

00:19:01.860 --> 00:19:04.070
singing Him a song. 'You are beautiful

00:19:04.080 --> 00:19:07.250
beyond

00:19:07.250 --> 00:19:07.260
description.'You

00:19:07.260 --> 00:19:09.890
just start singing to Him.

00:19:09.900 --> 00:19:15.650
'Father, I stand, I stand in awe

00:19:15.650 --> 00:19:15.660
of you.'Just

00:19:15.660 --> 00:19:17.450
start singing to Him.

00:19:17.460 --> 00:19:22.669
'I stand, I stand in awe of you,

00:19:22.679 --> 00:19:25.570
holy God to

00:19:25.570 --> 00:19:25.580
whom all

00:19:25.580 --> 00:19:29.390
praise is

00:19:29.390 --> 00:19:29.400
due.

00:19:29.400 --> 00:19:35.270
I stand in awe

00:19:35.270 --> 00:19:35.280
of you.'Worship

00:19:35.280 --> 00:19:38.330
Him. Worship Him. I

00:19:38.330 --> 00:19:38.340
start

00:19:38.340 --> 00:19:40.190
feeling His presence; He starts filling

00:19:40.200 --> 00:19:43.370
the house. 'Oh Lord, you're beautiful. Oh,

00:19:43.380 --> 00:19:46.970
you're worthy. Oh, you're worthy, Lord.

00:19:46.980 --> 00:19:50.750
You're worthy to be

00:19:50.760 --> 00:19:53.029
praised.'God,

00:19:53.039 --> 00:19:56.090
thank you, Jesus. And the more you do that,

00:19:56.100 --> 00:19:58.850
the more you practice His presence, the

00:19:58.860 --> 00:20:00.289
more He starts to come

00:20:00.299 --> 00:20:01.970
and the more He feels comfortable being

00:20:01.980 --> 00:20:05.090
around you. The Holy Spirit's a gentleman.

00:20:05.100 --> 00:20:08.029
He is not going to force Himself on you.

00:20:08.039 --> 00:20:10.370
He goes where He's invited.

00:20:10.380 --> 00:20:12.230
People, you need to understand:

00:20:12.240 --> 00:20:15.370
He loves each and every single one of us.

00:20:15.380 --> 00:20:19.190
He loves us and He wants to come and be

00:20:19.200 --> 00:20:22.250
in your house, but a lot of times the

00:20:22.260 --> 00:20:23.990
atmosphere is not conducive for Him

00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:26.090
because you've got all kinds of trash

00:20:26.100 --> 00:20:28.010
going on in your home.

00:20:28.020 --> 00:20:30.590
I'm telling you: make the atmosphere

00:20:30.600 --> 00:20:32.210
perfect,

00:20:32.220 --> 00:20:35.150
make the house perfect

00:20:35.160 --> 00:20:38.770
in the spirit realm by worship. He loves

00:20:38.780 --> 00:20:42.230
worship. Worship Him, and I'm telling you

00:20:42.240 --> 00:20:43.730
He'll come in your house and abide with

00:20:43.740 --> 00:20:46.070
you. And He's great; He'll come. You'll be in

00:20:46.080 --> 00:20:47.210
there, and all of a sudden you start

00:20:47.220 --> 00:20:51.010
worshiping the Lord. Hallelujah!

00:20:51.020 --> 00:20:52.610
Hallelujah!

00:20:52.620 --> 00:20:55.190
Oh Lord, I praise You!

00:20:55.200 --> 00:20:57.110
They don't have to be anything serious;

00:20:57.120 --> 00:21:00.049
just sing to Him: 'Oh God, You're so good

00:21:00.059 --> 00:21:03.230
to me, thank You for all You've

00:21:03.230 --> 00:21:03.240
done.'And

00:21:03.240 --> 00:21:05.690
you start worshiping Him,

00:21:05.700 --> 00:21:07.730
and I'm telling you—I've said it

00:21:07.730 --> 00:21:07.740
before—when

00:21:07.740 --> 00:21:10.549
you get real, God has to get real

00:21:10.559 --> 00:21:13.130
with you. And so, you know, I really

00:21:13.140 --> 00:21:15.409
thought that these prayer tips

00:21:15.419 --> 00:21:18.830
might help you. This is a walk; this is a

00:21:18.840 --> 00:21:22.190
way of life for me. This is how I live my

00:21:22.200 --> 00:21:25.330
life. I stay in an attitude of gratitude.

00:21:25.340 --> 00:21:29.090
I take the care out of my prayer. I try

00:21:29.100 --> 00:21:31.490
so hard to not let the devil come in

00:21:31.500 --> 00:21:34.430
with thoughts of fear. I feed on the word.

00:21:34.440 --> 00:21:37.669
Get in the word—priority number one

00:21:37.679 --> 00:21:40.549
above all of it. Get in the word. If you

00:21:40.559 --> 00:21:43.130
abide in Me and My words abide in you,

00:21:43.140 --> 00:21:45.110
you shall ask what you will and it shall

00:21:45.120 --> 00:21:48.409
be done. Remember that; get that down on

00:21:48.419 --> 00:21:50.450
the inside of you. You've got to get that

00:21:50.460 --> 00:21:52.970
down, and it has to be a

00:21:52.980 --> 00:21:55.850
foundation of a rock—a

00:21:55.850 --> 00:21:55.860
rock-solid

00:21:55.860 --> 00:21:58.310
foundation of the word inside of you.

00:21:58.320 --> 00:22:00.289
Build your house on that so that

00:22:00.299 --> 00:22:02.330
when the winds and the waves and

00:22:02.340 --> 00:22:04.850
the storms come, it's not able to knock

00:22:04.860 --> 00:22:07.430
your house down. Remember that the devil

00:22:07.440 --> 00:22:10.490
always comes to kill, steal, and destroy,

00:22:10.500 --> 00:22:12.289
but you've just got to get the word down

00:22:12.299 --> 00:22:14.810
inside of you. And He that dwells in the

00:22:14.820 --> 00:22:16.909
secret place of the Most High shall

00:22:16.919 --> 00:22:19.970
abide in the shadow of the Almighty. Stay

00:22:19.980 --> 00:22:21.649
in that secret place;

00:22:21.659 --> 00:22:23.930
stay in that secret place of the shadow

00:22:23.940 --> 00:22:25.909
of the Almighty today. I love you guys.

00:22:25.919 --> 00:22:28.730
Put a smile on your face and a song in

00:22:28.740 --> 00:22:30.350
your heart, and I just thank you for

00:22:30.360 --> 00:22:32.810
being with my family here. If you all

00:22:32.820 --> 00:22:35.330
could please like and share this video,

00:22:35.340 --> 00:22:38.390
it really helps me to get the word out,

00:22:38.400 --> 00:22:40.490
to get the gospel out. I just want to

00:22:40.500 --> 00:22:43.010
tell you: Jesus loves you today. He loves

00:22:43.020 --> 00:22:44.270
you so much;

00:22:44.280 --> 00:22:46.610
I hope you realize that.

00:22:46.620 --> 00:22:48.470
Thank you for being a part of my family.

00:22:48.470 --> 00:22:48.480
God

00:22:48.480 --> 00:22:52.220
bless you and have a good day.

